\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav><main class=\"pt-20\"><div class=\"min-h-screen\"><section class=\"relative py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-charcoal overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\"><img alt=\"Lecture audience at Art Deco Society event\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-20\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6\"><div class=\"h-px w-16 bg-gold/40\"></div><div class=\"w-3 h-3 rotate-45 border border-gold/60\"></div><div class=\"h-px w-16 bg-gold/40\"></div></div><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl tracking-wide text-cream\">Lectures &amp; Tours</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto text-cream/70\">Free educational programs exploring Art Deco architecture, design, and history.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-cream\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm mb-12\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-6\"><div class=\"w-2 h-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-gold to-copper rounded-full shrink-0\"></div><div><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl text-charcoal\">Art Deco Afternoons</h2><p class=\"text-gold font-display tracking-wider uppercase text-sm mt-1\">Free Lecture Series</p></div></div><p class=\"text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl\">Join us for our popular free lecture series exploring Art Deco architecture, design, and history in the Palm Beaches. Expert speakers share fascinating stories of our architectural heritage, from the glamorous 1920s to the sleek Streamline Moderne era.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/60\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin text-gold shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">Cultural Council of Palm Beach County, 601 Lake Avenue, Lake Worth Beach, FL</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/60\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-gold shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">Various dates, check events</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/60\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail text-gold shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg><a href=\"mailto:Art@ArtDecoPB.org\" class=\"text-sm text-gold hover:text-copper transition-colors\">RSVP via email</a></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm mb-12\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-6\"><div class=\"w-2 h-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-copper to-gold rounded-full shrink-0\"></div><div><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl text-charcoal\">Walking Tours</h2><p class=\"text-gold font-display tracking-wider uppercase text-sm mt-1\">Guided Architectural Tours</p></div></div><p class=\"text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl\">Explore the Art Deco architectural gems of the Palm Beaches on guided walking tours led by ADSPB President Sharon Koskoff and other knowledgeable guides. See eyebrows, ziggurats, racing stripes, and other distinctive Art Deco elements that make our buildings special.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/60\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar text-gold shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">Available by appointment and for special events</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/60\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail text-gold shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg><a href=\"mailto:Art@ArtDecoPB.org?subject=Walking Tour Request\" class=\"text-sm text-gold hover:text-copper transition-colors\">Book a tour</a></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-12\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3]\"><img alt=\"Sharon Koskoff speaking at ICADS lecture\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsharon-koskoff-icads-lecture.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsharon-koskoff-icads-lecture.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsharon-koskoff-icads-lecture.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3]\"><img alt=\"Audience enjoying a lecture\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience-2.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience-2.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-audience-2.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3]\"><img alt=\"Art Deco Afternoons lecture series\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-series-flyer.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-series-flyer.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flecture-series-flyer.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"bg-charcoal rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 text-center\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl text-cream mb-3\">Watch Our Lectures Online</h3><p class=\"text-cream/60 mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto\">Can&#x27;t attend in person? Watch recorded lectures on our YouTube channel featuring Art Deco architecture and public art.</p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC627yKy-KUfy58IJ2bQDpAg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gold text-charcoal px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-display tracking-wider uppercase text-sm hover:bg-cream transition-colors\">Visit YouTube Channel</a></div></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"relative bg-charcoal text-cream overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-5\"><svg class=\"w-full h-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><defs><pattern id=\"deco-fan\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><path d=\"M10 20 Q10 10, 0 0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0.3\" class=\"text-gold\"></path><path d=\"M10 20 Q10 10, 20 0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0.3\" class=\"text-gold\"></path><path d=\"M10 20 Q10 10, 5 0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0.2\" class=\"text-gold\"></path><path d=\"M10 20 Q10 10, 15 0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0.2\" class=\"text-gold\"></path><path d=\"M10 20 Q10 10, 10 0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0.2\" class=\"text-gold\"></path></pattern></defs><rect width=\"100\" height=\"100\" fill=\"url(#deco-fan)\"></rect></svg></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><img alt=\"ADSPB Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-full border-2 border-gold/30\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo-adspb-small.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo-adspb-small.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo-adspb-small.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75\"/><div><p class=\"font-display text-cream text-sm tracking-widest uppercase\">ADSPB</p><p class=\"text-gold/60 text-xs\">Est. <!-- -->1987</p></div></div><p class=\"text-cream/60 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs\">The Art Deco Society of the Palm Beaches promotes education, preservation and awareness of Twentieth Century Art, Architecture &amp; Design in the Palm Beaches.</p><div class=\"flex gap-4 mt-6\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC627yKy-KUfy58IJ2bQDpAg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-cream/40 hover:text-gold transition-colors\" aria-label=\"YouTube\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-youtube\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.5 17a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0-10 2 2 0 0 1 1.4-1.4 49.56 49.56 0 0 1 16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 21.5 7a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0 10 2 2 0 0 1-1.4 1.4 49.55 49.55 0 0 1-16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 2.5 17\"></path><path d=\"m10 15 5-3-5-3z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ArtDecoSocietyPalmBeaches\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-cream/40 hover:text-gold transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Facebook\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-facebook\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1